application_type_full: Prior Approval: Roof mounted solar PV on non-domestic building
description: Installation of roof mounted solar PV panels with a system capacity of 0.7 kWp, including all associated ancillary infrastructure (west roofslope, main building London South East Colleges Bromley Campus). (56 day application under Class J, Part 14, Schedule 2 of the General Permitted Development Order to determine whether prior approval is required as to the design or external appearance of solar photovoltaic equipment on the roof of a non-domestic building, with particular regard to the impact of glare on occupiers of neighbouring land).
site_name: London South East Colleges Bromley Campus
